review:
pros:
- nice naval battles with tons of guns;
- massive campaign scale with multiple theaters;
- nice period of time with gunpowder, guns, enlightenment ideas, colonies etc;
- you can build plantations.

cons:
- buggy as fuck;
- full of bugs;
- terrbile sound;
- terrible AI
- did I mentioned the shitload of bugs?

overall: nice game, especially if you like the time period. highly recommend to play with mods
